text: Chukadybashevo () is a rural locality (a selo) in Chukadybashevsky Selsoviet, Tuymazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 359 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 49 km from Tuymazy, 5 km from Alexeyevka. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tuymazinsky District
title: Chukadybashevo
